This paper discusses the mitigation of DDoS attacks, which is a common topic in the computer security (cs.CR) and networking (cs.NI) fields. The focus on private clouds suggests that the paper may also fall under the distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) category. The discussion of approaches and challenges to mitigate DDoS attacks also suggests that the paper may fall under the software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SI) categories.
